<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Soil Classification</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>

<header class="header">
    <h1>GLA MANTHAN 3.0 (2025)</h1>
    <h2>Soil Classification Dashboard</h2>
</header>

<div class="container">

    <div class="card description-card">
        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <p>
            This system uses a deep learning model to classify soil types from uploaded images.
            It analyzes texture, color, and visual patterns to identify the soil category and 
            returns a detailed description, recommended crops, and seasonal suitability.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card upload-card">
        <h2>Upload Soil Image</h2>
        <form action="/predict" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <label class="file-label">
                <input type="file" name="image" required />
            </label>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Analyze Soil</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="card error">
            <%= error %>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <% if (result) { %>
        <div class="card result-box">
            <h2>Prediction Result</h2>
            <div class="result-item"><strong>Soil Type:</strong> <%= result.soil_type %></div>
            <div class="result-item"><strong>Confidence:</strong> <%= (result.confidence * 100).toFixed(2) %>%</div>
            <div class="result-item"><strong>Description:</strong> <%= result.description %></div>
            <div class="result-item"><strong>Recommended Crops:</strong> <%= result.recommended_crops %></div>
            <div class="result-item"><strong>Best Season:</strong> <%= result.best_season %></div>
        </div>
    <% } %>

</div>

<footer class="footer">
